{
  "info": {
    "name": "BackendVetApp v2",
    "description": "API backend veterinaria — v2 (reestructurada).\n\n## Flujo recomendado\n1. `POST /auth/register` o `POST /auth/login` → guarda `access_token`.\n2. `POST /patients` → crea paciente.\n3. `POST /consultation/process` (audio o text_input) con `patient_id` y `section=anamnesis` → crea consulta, guarda sección híbrida.\n4. Continuar con demás secciones usando `consultation_id`.\n5. Editar textos manuales con `PATCH /consultation/:id/sections/:section`.\n6. Pausar/reanudar con `PATCH /consultation/:id/pause` y `/resume`.\n7. Firmar con `PATCH /consultation/:id/sign` (reemplaza /close).\n\n## Respuesta estándar\n`{ data, meta, error }` — `error` es `null` en éxito; `{code, message, details}` en fallo.\n\n## Secciones válidas (9)\nanamnesis, examen_fisico, problemas, abordaje_diagnostico, examenes_complementarios, diagnostico_presuntivo, diagnostico_definitivo, plan_terapeutico, pronostico_evolucion.\n\n## Auth\nTodos los endpoints excepto `/auth/*` requieren header `Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}`. Scripts auto-guardan el token tras login/register.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "veterinarian_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patient_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appointment_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "attachment_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/", "auth": { "type": "noauth" } }
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.veterinarian?.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('veterinarian_id', body.data.veterinarian.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"vet.test@vetapp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\",\n  \"full_name\": \"Luis Mena\",\n  \"license_number\": \"MV-12345\",\n  \"phone\": \"+57 300 0000000\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.session?.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.data.session.access_token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body?.data?.veterinarian?.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('veterinarian_id', body.data.veterinarian.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"vet.test@vetapp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/login"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Veterinarians",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/veterinarians/me" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Patients",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('patient_id', body.data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Luna\",\n  \"species\": \"dog\",\n  \"breed\": \"Labrador\",\n  \"sex\": \"female\",\n  \"age_years\": 4,\n  \"weight_kg\": 18.5,\n  \"owner_name\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"owner_phone\": \"+57 300 1111111\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/patients"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/patients?limit=20&offset=0",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["patients"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter", "value": "all", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "offset", "value": "0" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get by ID",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/{{patient_id}}" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"weight_kg\": 19.0\n}" },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/{{patient_id}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Favorites List",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/favorites" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Favorite Add",
          "request": { "method": "POST", "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/favorites/{{patient_id}}" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Favorite Remove",
          "request": { "method": "DELETE", "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/favorites/{{patient_id}}" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Alert Create",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"label\": \"Alergia a penicilina\",\n  \"severity\": \"warning\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/{{patient_id}}/alerts"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Alert List",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/patients/{{patient_id}}/alerts" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Appointments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Today",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/appointments/today" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('appointment_id', body.data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patient_id\": \"{{patient_id}}\",\n  \"scheduled_at\": \"2026-04-22T15:00:00Z\",\n  \"reason\": \"Control anual\",\n  \"urgent\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/appointments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"completed\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/appointments/{{appointment_id}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete",
          "request": { "method": "DELETE", "url": "{{base_url}}/appointments/{{appointment_id}}" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Consultation — Process Sections",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Anamnesis (audio, crea consulta)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.consultation_id) pm.collectionVariables.set('consultation_id', body.data.consultation_id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "audio", "type": "file", "src": [] },
                { "key": "section", "value": "anamnesis", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "patient_id", "value": "{{patient_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_type", "value": "routine", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "chief_complaint", "value": "Vómito agudo", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Examen Físico (texto)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "examen_fisico", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Mucosas rosadas, frecuencia cardiaca 120, peso 18.5 kg, abdomen blando.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Problemas",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "problemas", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Vómito agudo de 12 horas. Sin diarrea. Apetito disminuido.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Abordaje Diagnóstico",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "abordaje_diagnostico", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Sospecha de gastroenteritis. Solicitar hemograma y ecografía abdominal.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Exámenes Complementarios",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "examenes_complementarios", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Hemograma normal. Eco abdominal muestra leve gas en asas intestinales.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Diagnóstico Presuntivo",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "diagnostico_presuntivo", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Gastroenteritis inespecífica.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Diagnóstico Definitivo",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "diagnostico_definitivo", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Gastritis aguda confirmada por respuesta a tratamiento sintomático.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "8. Plan Terapéutico",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "plan_terapeutico", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Ayuno 12h, maropitant 1mg/kg SC, sueroterapia de mantenimiento, dieta blanda 5 días.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "9. Pronóstico y Evolución",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "section", "value": "pronostico_evolucion", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "consultation_id", "value": "{{consultation_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "text_input", "value": "Pronóstico favorable. Control en 48 horas.", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/process"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Consultation — Management",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Edit Section Text",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"text\": \"Texto editado manualmente por el veterinario.\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/sections/anamnesis"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Pause",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"labs\",\n  \"note\": \"Esperando resultados de laboratorio\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/pause"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Resume",
          "request": { "method": "PATCH", "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/resume" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"result\": \"discharge\",\n  \"summary\": \"Paciente estable, tratamiento sintomático.\",\n  \"primary_diagnosis\": \"Gastritis aguda\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/sign"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Consultation — Attachments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body?.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('attachment_id', body.data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [] },
                { "key": "section", "value": "examenes_complementarios", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "label", "value": "Hemograma PDF", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/attachments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/attachments" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/consultation/{{consultation_id}}/attachments/{{attachment_id}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Dashboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Consultations Recent",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/consultations/recent?limit=4",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["consultations", "recent"],
              "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "4" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Consultations by Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/consultations?status=paused",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["consultations"],
              "query": [{ "key": "status", "value": "paused" }]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
